[{"id":"VR629757","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"passage\"><div class=\"prose style:1\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows two blocks on a horizontal surface. The blocks move to the right at a speed of v. The block on the left has mass m and the block on the right has mass 2 m. A compressed horizontal spring extends from the right side of the left block to the left side of the right block. Above the spring is a release mechanism that connects the two blocks.\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/578/VR629757.g03.svg\"/></div></div></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Two blocks, one of mass <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"m\"><math alttext=\"m\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>m</mi></math></span></span> and the other of mass <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2 m\"><math alttext=\"2 m\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn><mi>m</mi></math></span></span>, are initially sliding to the right on a horizontal surface with speed <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"v\"><math alttext=\"v\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>v</mi></math></span></span> and total kinetic energy <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"K sub i\"><math alttext=\"K sub i\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>K</mi><mi>i</mi></msub></math></span></span>. There is negligible friction between the blocks and the surface. A compressed spring with negligible mass is held in place between the blocks by a remote‑controlled release mechanism, also of negligible mass. The mechanism is activated, releasing the blocks. The spring expands, pushing the blocks apart. The block of mass <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"m\"><math alttext=\"m\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>m</mi></math></span></span> comes to a complete stop and the block of mass <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2 m\"><math alttext=\"2 m\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn><mi>m</mi></math></span></span> continues moving to the right. The total kinetic energy of the two-block system is <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"K sub f\"><math alttext=\"K sub f\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>K</mi><mi>f</mi></msub></math></span></span>. What is the ratio <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"K sub f to K sub i\"><math alttext=\"K sub f to K sub i\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>K</mi><mi>f</mi></msub><mo>:</mo><msub><mi>K</mi><mi>i</mi></msub></math></span></span> ?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VR629757_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2 to 3\"><math alttext=\"2 to 3\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>3</mn></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1 to 1\"><math alttext=\"1 to 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>1</mn></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"3 to 2\"><math alttext=\"3 to 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>3</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>2</mn></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"9 to 2\"><math alttext=\"9 to 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>9</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>2</mn></math></span></span></p>"],"answer":2}]